AMG Review by John Bush
   In 2003, Collectables released Flute Fever/Monium, which contained 
   two complete albums -- the classic Flute Fever (1963, originally 
   released on Columbia) and Monium (1974, also originally released on 
   Columbia) -- by Jeremy Steig on one compact disc.
